	('17692e48-406c-4e08-bdfe-8b2ad3ab1554', 'Delivering Constructive Criticism', 'CORP127', 'This corporate training program on Delivering Constructive Criticism helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying delivering constructive criticism in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765257974604-m487n3i8f9k.jpg', 'Active', '5 weeks', 4, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-23 12:26:06.938928+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Delivering Constructive Criticism in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong delivering constructive criticism is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to delivering constructive criticism in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in delivering constructive criticism.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Delivering Constructive Criticism, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.011715937,0.037055615,0.01949666,0.017451305,-0.025022708,0.0059476774,-0.0065248027,0.03889763,0.027965149,0.054255735,0.05645659,-0.025859987,-0.014867699,-0.03310844,0.05124153,0.03583558,0.02379071,-0.019030176,0.038060352,0.046265695,0.08387152,0.032151546,0.034830842,0.06650394,-0.00087017304,-0.0069972677,-0.0018270643,0.017666606,0.007421888,-0.018659381,-0.008665847,-0.00055058626,-0.0067640254,-0.04200753,0.04999757,0.05248549,-0.009216059,0.052868243,0.02923303,0.027749848,-0.015573406,0.033586886,-0.00043097488,0.0031487704,-0.052054886,-0.005388494,-0.03428063,0.0012432111,0.0072783544,0.0060852305,-0.021936733,0.044064846,0.0039770794,0.026553733,-0.026458044,-0.026266666,-0.044399757,0.044280145,-0.02