	('bf93db2a-c5b7-4329-b414-15cba38267ea', 'Motivating Your Sales Team', 'CORP086', 'This corporate training program on Motivating Your Sales Team helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying motivating your sales team in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765255058684-e59kc41zcxv.jpg', 'Active', '6 weeks', 4, 0, 0, 9, 9, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-29 09:06:44.221772+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Motivating Your Sales Team in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong motivating your sales team is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to motivating your sales team in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in motivating your sales team.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Motivating Your Sales Team, Sales Skills, Customer Focus, Negotiation, Collaboration, Teamwork, Facilitation, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.013021461,0.0282365,0.029379962,-0.00019744402,-0.037850913,0.0067265877,0.018178705,0.040651225,0.025459522,0.01239139,0.08568961,-0.026299616,-0.030523423,-0.037757568,0.017315276,0.002985543,-0.004518423,-0.016860224,-0.010034459,-0.01607847,0.03533063,0.031013478,0.010215312,0.08573628,-0.034630552,0.04989226,-0.018365392,0.03659077,-0.016591862,-0.018552082,-0.00026836342,-0.024269389,-0.06347378,-0.0406979,0.026416296,0.016265158,-0.019135479,0.013674867,0.010337826,0.006936611,0.0088384915,0.0032495311,0.058059845,0.05353267,-0.0059681693,0.016101805,0.0053701857,-0.042448096,0.012228038,-0.0040983763,-0.05572625,0.03278701,0.024712771,-0.01941551,-0.05035898,0.0064232205,-0.00902517