	('c4bab14d-b626-4ce3-908b-ff052822eb3a', 'Respect In The Workplace', 'CORP133', 'This corporate training program on Respect In The Workplace helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying respect in the workplace in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765212640193-28re30ggowv.jpg', 'Active', '3 weeks', 4, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-23 10:18:00.014812+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Respect In The Workplace in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong respect in the workplace is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to respect in the workplace in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in respect in the workplace.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Respect In The Workplace, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.010874009,0.023163088,0.055628527,0.04342644,0.00064156647,-0.037766155,-0.009830103,0.05460782,0.0031433133,0.048947535,0.07335171,-0.009638721,0.007481318,-0.036745448,0.017143236,0.012526858,0.013002414,0.008693407,0.02400981,0.009087771,0.022188777,0.010705824,-0.029182939,0.08578578,-0.030969176,0.012155691,-0.01590215,0.061242417,-0.0026170113,-0.0053935084,0.030667603,-0.017595595,-0.025958434,-0.009377745,0.042916086,-0.019022265,-0.018593105,0.018326329,0.009255956,0.0042278143,-0.015159817,0.037580572,0.017688386,0.03813732,-0.03157232,0.0065939985,-0.016609685,-0.026051225,0.03410089,0.015600577,-0.011836721,0.008049666,-0.026074423,-0.006709988,-0.03683824,0.004778764,-0.011529349,0.01700405,-0.032059476,-0.012016504,0.03366013,-0.03871727,-0.023128292,0.0087746,-0.00075393