	('9f6b4a31-e12d-45b9-923e-93671abdd18d', 'Networking Within the Company', 'CORP131', 'This corporate training program on Networking Within the Company helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying networking within the company in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765211786510-8knmjjjw76i.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:02.702593+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Networking Within the Company in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong networking within the company is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to networking within the company in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in networking within the company.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Networking Within the Company, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.028181123,0.011887024,0.056748617,0.012225102,0.012339806,0.0060853837,0.030595958,0.08601642,-0.008590775,0.062834,0.05336785,-0.0098947855,0.00041504976,-0.0151893115,0.023882717,-0.0077938796,-0.02967832,0.018328596,0.018159559,0.0037248828,0.06365505,0.039289363,0.0134023335,0.05819752,0.013655891,-0.00015979414,-0.021021137,0.073459275,0.013197073,-0.029364392,0.027094448,-0.022264777,-0.047934473,0.001937905,0.02501769,0.018014668,-0.0017341533,0.03610178,0.021105656,0.018256152,-0.012472622,-0.007027169,0.035135847,0.03187582,-0.030813294,-0.0024450202,-0.03421821,0.0033988801,0.061143618,0.014899531,-0.05892197,0.005877104,-0.012798625,-0.04107634,-0.072493345,0.019016825,0.00024431336,-0.016432952,-0.040931452,0.02435361,0.034894362,-0.0