	('fa52fc84-88f7-44e6-bad5-1af2a14ca009', 'Accountability in the Workplace', 'CORP001', 'This corporate training program on Accountability in the Workplace helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying accountability in the workplace in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765168743502-g2icy5a6sb7.webp', 'Active', '2 weeks', 4, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:55:35.433987+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Accountability in the Workplace in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong accountability in the workplace is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to accountability in the workplace in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in accountability in the workplace.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Accountability in the Workplace, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.003403792,0.03072738,0.07064034,0.04019272,-0.0054699634,-0.0028719495,0.034201115,0.03436431,0.02236944,0.027883116,0.09502641,-0.032429278,0.005956636,-0.047140185,-0.005694357,0.004514104,0.008427882,-0.014617654,-0.02064423,0.0053475667,-0.006836726,0.023826543,0.0065511335,0.09418712,-0.04741995,-0.03450419,-0.023348613,-0.016016472,-0.0025615864,-0.017438605,0.04634752,-0.019280383,-0.037325144,-0.010106464,0.046300896,0.010566909,-0.005096945,0.027416844,0.048725512,0.0058109253,-0.027393531,0.023709975,0.053341616,0.049844567,-0.011913272,0.0428971,0.0054408214,-0.012216349,0.014431145,0.035203602,-0.003505789,0.05096362,0.02112216,-0.0093138,-0.03483058,0.04518184,-0.0062363995,0.028046312,-0.049191788,0.006994093,0.03564