	('b6fc636d-acf6-4121-a4e3-8e2bf34f9d44', 'Building Confidence and Assertiveness', 'CORP013', 'This corporate training program on Building Confidence and Assertiveness helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying building confidence and assertiveness in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765170073236-0vwvhh09ysmr.webp', 'Active', '2 weeks', 1, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:56:02.329501+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Building Confidence and Assertiveness in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong building confidence and assertiveness is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to building confidence and assertiveness in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in building confidence and assertiveness.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Building Confidence and Assertiveness, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.009598037,0.012390985,0.07578904,0.04319428,-0.027046187,0.007545314,0.0017961331,0.017665863,0.01927072,0.050136216,0.05638147,-0.041651625,0.012938378,-0.056729812,0.024657564,0.038491677,0.016421787,-0.010755027,-0.0043822536,-0.008366403,0.05264925,0.009952599,-0.009598037,0.039263003,-0.033639785,0.006127069,-0.0119804405,0.013037904,0.0041520996,-0.020726288,0.0073213805,-0.025876757,-0.0032656966,0.019308042,0.029360166,0.028066328,-0.011314861,-0.00075849687,0.05369427,-0.0015714221,-0.018325223,0.005517472,0.014020723,0.03577959,0.006136399,4.7964917e-05,0.028041447,0.024159934,0.020415269,0.022803891,-0.016844774,0.018350104,0.03276893,0.016919417,-0.028364906,-0.002898694