	('33b4d45f-36d2-45fc-ace6-8eab101cc8ff', 'Business Succession Planning', 'CORP030', 'This corporate training program on Business Succession Planning helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying business succession planning in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765257898727-zi4bfvqwwbh.jpg', 'Active', '6 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:56:17.114335+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Business Succession Planning in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong business succession planning is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to business succession planning in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in business succession planning.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Business Succession Planning, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.007158243,0.045695886,0.07970484,0.009028152,-0.024893155,0.00926189,0.018558841,0.06315616,0.036112607,0.012727064,0.03480367,-0.019271744,0.016957732,-0.047729414,0.0084496485,0.061099257,0.0012190926,0.008321092,0.033798594,-0.0087067615,0.06610126,0.0010788495,-0.011505781,0.06965409,-0.021410452,0.02167925,-0.0007048678,0.03153133,-0.018710772,-0.05488181,0.072599195,-0.01162265,-0.045719262,0.006743357,0.027020177,0.0033599916,-0.023876393,0.015134571,0.0014513703,0.029264066,-0.042563792,0.0061648544,0.026926681,0.023841333,0.034897167,0.011067521,-0.031507958,0.0045257625,0.0070355306,0.020417063,-0.0021138731,0.004718597,-0.014176243,0.004759501,-0.050487526,0.019038005,-0.010436427,-0.047916405,-0.05637774,0.0055249953,0.04983306,-0.044784307,0.