	('e92dae47-bf15-4e6e-836f-f7cf6c0c30b8', 'High Performance Teams Inside the Company', 'CORP080', 'This corporate training program on High Performance Teams Inside the Company helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying high performance teams inside the company in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765254987615-j4oikvov9h.jpg', 'Active', '6 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 6, 6, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:58:48.761801+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of High Performance Teams Inside the Company in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong high performance teams inside the company is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to high performance teams inside the company in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in high performance teams inside the company.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: High Performance Teams Inside the Company, Collaboration, Teamwork, Facilitation, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.014368116,0.0063052555,0.07040254,0.031096093,0.015535756,-0.01882973,-0.0071963486,0.07055003,-0.0037641022,0.016863178,0.07310655,-0.008966245,-0.013618368,-0.028883724,0.022246612,0.0094578825,-0.011319961,-0.028342921,0.009334973,0.012807165,0.047320142,0.020316934,-0.012979239,0.060373127,-0.009992539,0.0014288224,-0.02637637,0.055653404,0.0153145185,-0.023549452,0.04107634,-0.015400555,-0.0054049436,-0.052261103,0.02468022,0.014110005,-0.0013689041,0.085643314,0.0145893525,0.022111412,-0.012708838,0.019395113,0.012598219,0.031907294,-0.0031864278,-0.017563762,0.012438437,-0.018301219,0.012481456,0.008087442,-