	('10b295c6-e4e1-47b4-8511-a90107b44922', 'Critical Thinking', 'CORP057', 'This corporate training program on Critical Thinking helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying critical thinking in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765258770673-rtdc9i7krcd.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:56:50.53779+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Critical Thinking in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong critical thinking is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to critical thinking in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in critical thinking.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Critical Thinking, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.005311711,0.018695787,0.04177508,0.010725225,0.003754727,-0.01762985,-0.004281706,0.061225407,0.0051110997,0.079717584,0.06845939,-0.02460035,-0.004383509,-0.023977555,0.0336069,0.014923094,-0.006910614,-0.027355013,0.020576144,0.0412481,0.047332317,0.02444465,-0.022851735,0.063524954,-0.034828536,0.009952721,-0.006910614,0.026756173,-0.0302534,-0.0030421074,0.055907708,-0.011108483,-0.032409225,-0.009749116,0.012611572,0.036672965,-0.021522311,0.030037817,0.036672965,0.033367366,-0.008880798,-0.0010030571,0.014108672,0.029486883,-0.030181538,-0.036361568,-0.0036020228,0.0067070085,0.011653427,0.030037817,-0.04548789,0.013952973,-0.010785109,-0.0038774894,-0.04967977,-0.0036169938,-0.05207513,0.027546642,-0.02058812,-0.0068447418,0.07008824,-0.05126071,0.017546013,0.05059001,0.0039224024,0.022145106,-0.0076771295,-0.018659856,-0.034349464,-0