	('60382df5-3224-4d9d-827f-2a3561e35b59', 'Creative Problem Solving', 'CORP015', 'This corporate training program on Creative Problem Solving helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying creative problem solving in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765170320108-rcg7zsg0x1i.webp', 'Active', '2 weeks', 5, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-27 09:36:09.398322+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Creative Problem Solving in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong creative problem solving is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to creative problem solving in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in creative problem solving.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Creative Problem Solving, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.025654618,0.011262109,0.060847178,0.011561697,-0.024651911,-0.04296965,0.003371907,0.0550755,0.01694819,0.04304302,0.059624366,-0.04932828,-0.024492946,-0.012215902,0.012454351,0.013903385,-0.034043115,-0.021937266,0.018036492,-0.014294685,0.03827405,0.018782409,-0.021680476,0.07796656,-0.0142335445,0.020090818,0.0090365885,0.038836543,0.017743018,0.010039295,0.034923542,-0.013560997,-0.056934178,-0.012533834,0.018134318,0.035021365,-0.022805464,0.022414163,-0.012093621,0.008143935,0.0049646213,-0.0022163487,0.022279654,0.025483424,-0.010253288,-0.037515905,-0.00060643884,0.0217783,-0.015872113,0.012851765,-0.0013749005,0.071069896,0.014612616,-0.018440021,-0.06422214,-0.019308219,-0.015065057,-0.010675158,-0.026852975,0.023001114,0.102422826,-0.04945056,0.02558125,0.009531828,0.009360