	('8ad4774c-12e7-49c7-b64b-a7125ee82608', 'Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion', 'CORP034', 'This corporate training program on Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying diversity, equity, and inclusion in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765258088124-1j3p63v8vuc.jpg', 'Active', '4 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:57:10.695953+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong diversity, equity, and inclusion is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to diversity, equity, and inclusion in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in diversity, equity, and inclusion.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.0048624794,0.014363741,0.054393835,0.025124772,0.022617005,-0.0019853162,0.03190634,0.057266586,-0.0045328196,0.039794624,0.05557119,-0.010996503,-0.00630474,-0.0538758,0.05166237,0.014646306,0.008329792,-0.0014481476,0.0037999158,0.05811428,0.037369274,0.02776205,-0.0090479795,0.11114238,-0.007352587,-0.011685256,-0.014010534,0.04749453,-0.003523237,0.0054217232,0.04546948,-0.0126918955,-0.049778603,-0.034920372,0.01942637,0.026255034,-0.02882167,0.046246536,0.025689904,-0.018048864,-0.016329924,0.03216536,0.0016659584,0.013645553,-0.029763553,-0.019579427,0.022664098,0.0012428461,0.03150604,0.017754525,-0.00996043,0.0071406625,0.0017159961,4.550756e-05,-0.037816666,0.041513566,-0.001692449,-0.007852963,-0.040524587,-0.029