	('6d5ebaf2-3576-43b1-a0f3-4d2ca806e1e8', 'Archiving and Records Management', 'CORP004', 'This corporate training program on Archiving and Records Management helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying archiving and records management in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765170003213-jbs55iyu8x.webp', 'Active', '5 weeks', 1, 0, 0, 6, 6, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:55:47.679547+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Archiving and Records Management in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong archiving and records management is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to archiving and records management in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in archiving and records management.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Archiving and Records Management, Leadership, People Management, Decision Making, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'technical', NULL, '[0.012119335,0.08296571,0.08253007,-0.020947149,0.00899723,0.039304644,0.029817315,-0.0053456975,-0.0044532353,0.036182538,0.026719412,-0.042886592,0.0036243044,-0.026017545,0.011665541,0.012191942,0.008537385,-0.010316258,0.020305786,0.0020798908,0.051841468,0.024456492,0.00059220166,0.056681942,-0.014654533,-0.010878963,-0.031971328,0.037320048,0.017812941,-0.039522465,-0.009953223,0.0057692393,-0.034899812,0.009336063,0.037271645,0.011066532,-0.015368503,0.0037271644,0.015477413,0.00695213,0.025896532,-0.008688649,0.017849246,0.050389327,0.015416907,0.010721648,-0.0074906326,0.015767843,0.01074585,0.051066995,-0.016953757,0.027082449,0.021515904,-0.012143537,-0.021092363,