	('9b71ceb9-3eff-4b2e-b585-35ae061b0a0d', 'Organizational Skills', 'CORP010', 'This corporate training program on Organizational Skills helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying organizational skills in their daily roles.', 'data:image/png;base64,', 'Active', '4 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 6, 6, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:08.269747+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Organizational Skills in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong organizational skills is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to organizational skills in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in organizational skills.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Organizational Skills, Time Management, Prioritization, Planning, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.006969788,0.042336714,0.049588516,0.0101813,-0.0011935259,0.0050215856,0.002871944,0.05239715,0.009588494,0.02195109,0.034532394,-0.056633122,0.020512242,-0.04848348,0.036120884,0.01039425,-0.014273389,-0.015838858,0.039343905,0.012707921,0.06515112,-0.0005474823,-0.026083468,0.06690075,-0.011004322,0.019717997,-0.0024762603,0.050831683,-0.010008639,-0.0052805785,0.02310217,-0.021974113,-0.0248403,-0.013306482,0.028408648,0.020316558,-0.00023093537,0.031815846,0.006031658,0.011528064,0.0035683473,-0.00011214035,0.015769793,0.03160865,0.0134906545,0.019384183,-0.008287774,-0.027925195,0.017669074,0.036765486,-0.05239715,0.0031568361,-0.0006255399,-0.024333825,-0.03188491,0.0030647498,-0.033841744,-0.028523756,-0.045513693,0.016322311,0.06358565,-0.052166935,0.03416405,0.07546479,0.013686338,0.025853252,-0.013076266,-0.01891224,-0.0062964065,-0.039781317,0.053916