	('8bdef3cd-c7b7-4a49-9d7c-ceb5325c6bca', 'Personal Branding', 'CORP024', 'This corporate training program on Personal Branding helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying personal branding in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256840188-dn0a8l5kn3.webp', 'Active', '6 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:15.961955+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Personal Branding in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong personal branding is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to personal branding in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in personal branding.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Personal Branding, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.0034411428,0.023839423,0.063396096,0.021371624,-0.015501616,-0.022030503,0.005588488,0.0491164,0.021623196,0.04822991,0.07949669,-0.017382413,-0.012566611,-0.05558539,0.017070943,0.011464487,-0.013596857,-0.011823875,0.014279695,0.012219202,0.024198812,0.0032404845,-0.03991606,0.08793034,-0.04013169,0.018352762,-0.016471963,0.03229703,-0.024198812,0.0104222605,0.016388107,-0.026067631,-0.025253018,-0.004091037,0.0337825,0.025636366,0.003138658,0.021455482,0.03469295,0.036346138,-0.018556416,0.0008670243,0.037903488,0.049595587,0.010104801,0.019610621,0.008547451,0.03533985,0.039077487,0.043390147,-0.02760102,0.0029514765,0.0015011949,0.026642652,-0.06382736,0.021299746,-0.01504639,-0.007337511,-0.023551913,0.027816655,0.045306884,-0.034501277,0.008080247,0.07293186,0.006972133,-0.015058369,-0.01380051,-0.008517503,-0.00890085,-0.08922414,0.