	('a5b791e5-5cc9-4e08-b939-cef5b8eb199e', 'Project Management 7th Edition', 'CORP025', 'This corporate training program on Project Management 7th Edition helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying project management 7th edition in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765259041288-69vibuptxdm.webp', 'Active', '4 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 9, 9, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:23.713651+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Project Management 7th Edition in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong project management 7th edition is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to project management 7th edition in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in project management 7th edition.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Project Management 7th Edition, Leadership, People Management, Decision Making, Project Management, Risk Management, Stakeholder Management, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.035338517,0.064806096,0.059522253,-0.033667557,-0.027503075,0.011866064,-0.006458029,0.036196575,-0.017037004,-0.022445038,0.062773846,-0.026080502,-0.0044455403,-0.012261223,0.03330627,-0.0028028071,0.0018798284,-0.0030737736,0.0011748928,0.019351507,0.058348067,0.028338555,0.027299851,0.04367073,-0.036512703,0.047509417,-0.050715853,0.058664195,-0.010477362,0.045386847,0.022874068,-0.018832155,-0.017477324,0.011154777,0.02250149,-0.0031132894,-0.017578935,0.024003094,-0.031861115,0.024974057,0.0029100648,-0.020164406,0.009653172,0.048728764,0.00952898,-0.0095064,0.017228939,-0.005139891,0.047057807,0.059160966,0.02337084,-0.0204