	('87110f54-803a-4e59-8ff1-cbf1fefc6a83', 'Time Management', 'CORP029', 'This corporate training program on Time Management helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying time management in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256045211-8g8gnmtjam7.jpg', 'Active', '6 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 8, 8, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:01:24.352683+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Time Management in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong time management is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to time management in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in time management.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Time Management, Leadership, People Management, Decision Making, Prioritization, Planning, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.013477156,0.05472397,0.080335364,-0.016067073,-0.019556265,-0.013968761,0.017469944,0.061342645,0.021258894,0.019640198,0.048752774,-0.02582722,-0.02039559,-0.047841508,0.03434037,-0.0028327208,-0.022385988,-0.010407626,0.033860754,0.0529494,0.01257788,0.035827175,-0.019160584,0.0796639,-0.009760147,0.033189297,-0.011786517,0.049208406,-0.0032314,-0.00865104,0.03026365,-0.019124612,-0.012350063,0.009202596,0.04352498,0.036906306,0.016870426,0.041798368,-2.981195e-05,-0.015167796,-0.04659451,0.0217505,0.027098197,0.029016653,-0.016714552,0.005329712,0.0029001664,0.045347515,0.008920822,0.032877546,-0.020179763,-0.0010761342,-0.023477111,0.0155155165,-0.044795956,0.0068584816,-0.021822441,0.021270886,-0.009148639,0.010743356,0.04208614,-0.05270959,0.030359574,0.091702215,0.010509544,0.