	('0365c112-280c-4454-86d0-eda6925efbe4', 'Health and Wellness at Work', 'CORP039', 'This corporate training program on Health and Wellness at Work helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying health and wellness at work in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256157351-sbpc8myurr.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:58:46.999234+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Health and Wellness at Work in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong health and wellness at work is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to health and wellness at work in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in health and wellness at work.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Health and Wellness at Work, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.014813385,0.021024674,0.056898776,0.034912974,-0.019114433,0.0003243807,-0.010380182,0.031669166,0.029746912,0.033831704,0.037147596,-0.006589734,-0.023751875,-0.053486772,0.004913767,0.021613367,0.013467806,-0.02549392,0.019715138,0.015642358,0.022057887,0.033351142,-0.02303103,0.053342603,-0.044404116,-0.01954694,-0.032462098,0.018345531,-0.0016534405,0.0007032003,0.027536318,-0.0249653,-0.010332126,0.025950456,0.042553943,0.012386537,0.0060370853,0.03628258,0.023079086,0.013503849,-0.023283325,0.025974484,0.036931343,0.06876871,0.00250494,-0.014056497,-0.00010559268,0.019246588,0.039598472,0.014248722,-0.017901009,0.009917639,0.0028984016,-0.004718538,-0.033591423,0.0151257515,0.008602096,0.030900266,-0.057571568,0.014380878,0.06497225,-0.010302091,-0.01965506