	('1dd61e66-9db8-4425-9927-d90bf4340aae', 'Millennial Onboarding', 'CORP044', 'This corporate training program on Millennial Onboarding helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying millennial onboarding in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256357820-qlcfhf5qded.jpg', 'Active', '6 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:59:50.664436+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Millennial Onboarding in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong millennial onboarding is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to millennial onboarding in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in millennial onboarding.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Millennial Onboarding, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.015387697,0.060211606,0.024040861,0.01084221,-0.033428002,-0.026551824,0.041849386,0.041617602,0.025418673,0.041179795,0.059593525,-0.054236803,-0.033659782,-0.0056239134,0.009245494,-0.012632076,-0.038115133,-0.043626375,0.012928241,0.048081722,0.04888008,0.023319764,-0.0095094675,0.09096125,-0.013353173,0.016932905,-0.010900155,0.027607717,-0.009361385,-0.0068632993,0.037394036,-0.015902767,-0.08065986,-0.006901929,0.02956498,0.006016654,0.0016788042,0.017538112,-0.0018156194,0.034638412,-0.02581785,0.0024980863,0.054751873,0.0026606552,9.898989e-05,0.0050766524,0.0077839857,-0.00942577,0.019173456,0.0787026,-0.03134197,-0.0116148135,0.012084815,-0.0059941197,-0.048287753,0.023306888,-0.001746407,-0.0015773999,-0.020164965,0.023989355,0.04694857,-0.026281413,-0.016572356,0.054185297,0.03958308,0.0261784,-0.