	('f5078488-9e97-4599-9d52-be4015f28ce3', 'Being A Likeable Boss', 'CORP056', 'This corporate training program on Being A Likeable Boss helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying being a likeable boss in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256582559-tcj90ln4m1q.jpg', 'Active', '5 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:55:53.29537+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Being A Likeable Boss in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong being a likeable boss is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to being a likeable boss in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in being a likeable boss.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Being A Likeable Boss, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.02112246,-0.020593517,0.028962571,-0.003629137,-0.007746077,-0.035215855,-0.00086394034,0.007775463,0.0070290654,0.017126001,0.06314404,-0.044172622,0.030843258,-0.04751084,-0.0025697816,0.022380168,0.00014949987,-0.01696144,0.003823083,-0.0019776593,0.03326464,0.027293462,0.0076109027,0.053599562,-0.012882702,-0.012682879,-0.033076573,0.016561795,-0.033499725,-0.003038484,0.044172622,-0.025107164,-0.019135984,0.016644076,0.01191885,0.021192985,0.011125436,-0.0014354927,0.035639007,-0.0217807,-0.013611468,0.03970599,0.059993897,-0.0024096295,-0.023908226,-0.0016353156,0.04403157,0.0103085125,0.032935522,0.03016151,-0.0046047433,0.008598263,0.012835685,-0.007005557,-0.023908226,0.029620811,0.012835685,-0.016197411,-0.013188314,-0.007940023,0.035874095,-0.020805094,-0.026423644,0.054916043,-0.026588205,-0.0136232