	('f1f97ce4-7d0e-4ac9-a8c0-1a05ddc30da0', 'Improving Self-Awareness', 'CORP061', 'This corporate training program on Improving Self-Awareness helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying improving self-awareness in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256647638-42ufujcibq.jpg', 'Active', '3 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:58:57.570937+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Improving Self-Awareness in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong improving self-awareness is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to improving self-awareness in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in improving self-awareness.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Improving Self-Awareness, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.0028217782,0.023166187,0.056418486,0.04291721,-0.0051682796,-0.026661037,0.020422673,0.0566917,0.034174394,0.068622,0.06402291,-0.040572133,-0.0074507464,-0.04931495,0.056236345,0.022574225,-0.006682335,-0.0076158126,0.024748545,0.009972275,0.040048473,0.0039615887,-0.016278941,0.10017811,0.0047100787,-0.013603731,-0.015151938,0.026752107,-0.030850302,-0.0080313245,0.014047703,-0.02499899,-0.024976224,-0.005333346,-0.0009662064,0.038340893,0.0062668235,-0.00792887,-0.0012259011,-0.016017113,-0.020399906,0.006426198,0.0067164865,0.048358705,0.008685897,-0.030941373,0.017872684,0.021720434,0.0046474673,0.02804987,-0.06525237,0.012135211,-0.0054386463,-0.0073539834,0.003563153,0.013694802,-0.009181095,-0.006392046,-0.056646165,0.03745295,0.04881406,-0.034242697,-0.026547197,0.04309935,0.01