	('488b2c00-b07b-48c4-bb0c-afb18c1e0be2', 'Unconscious Bias', 'CORP048', 'This corporate training program on Unconscious Bias helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying unconscious bias in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256604550-wfoa03xsg4i.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:01:33.845038+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Unconscious Bias in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong unconscious bias is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to unconscious bias in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in unconscious bias.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Unconscious Bias, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.018324293,0.023363778,0.011147582,0.029824033,-0.005063771,-0.026618192,0.00997575,0.07757163,0.00961145,0.026812484,0.057899427,-0.043205988,0.04434746,-0.01976935,0.01663637,0.0049453736,-0.006013987,-0.00431392,-0.030892646,-0.0038039,0.03822722,0.010959361,0.011086865,0.10268405,-0.031232659,-0.017049244,0.020364374,0.03094122,-0.044468895,0.009016427,0.05595649,-0.019380763,-0.010200402,0.008943567,0.040364448,0.027832525,-0.02919258,0.025160993,0.0085853385,0.005024305,0.0023315204,-0.0027322506,0.028973999,-0.022671608,-0.042841688,0.041117337,-0.008093533,-0.0029159186,-0.00837283,0.029386872,-0.043813154,-0.0022176767,-0.036089994,0.0052550286,-0.015713476,0.017279968,-0.012495493,0.021056544,-0.014304849,-0.0051852046,0.051973477,-0.015859196,-0.020862252,0.044274602,0.0041196267,-0.023351634,0.0062416745,0.019599345,-0.061348133,-0.06338