	('204444ce-7447-4600-8ca6-15174fe55ea1', 'Increasing Your Happiness', 'CORP062', 'This corporate training program on Increasing Your Happiness helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying increasing your happiness in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765258831030-u6vzp6ydwrh.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:59:01.082497+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Increasing Your Happiness in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong increasing your happiness is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to increasing your happiness in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in increasing your happiness.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Increasing Your Happiness, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.009816612,0.0055489126,0.097492434,0.0371732,-0.00035263412,-0.01633696,0.03127842,0.07141104,-0.0027488922,0.026009211,0.05062292,0.019043747,-0.01928435,-0.036114547,0.015049733,0.024216717,0.016782077,-0.011001583,0.009010592,0.039627355,0.030725034,0.013858747,-0.0025248304,0.1023045,-0.016433202,0.005452671,-0.045594316,0.051344734,0.02069188,-0.008463219,0.009431647,-0.025696427,-0.016409142,-0.021209177,-0.0010827146,0.0429958,-0.02304979,0.037606288,0.0054045506,0.0006251925,0.0045654466,0.013750476,0.036210787,0.035729583,-0.014183561,-0.019115929,0.014027169,0.0083910385,-0.015013643,0.037534107,-0.025672367,-0.009179014,-0.00926924,0.001079707,-0.020343004,0.023362575,-0.00042180758,-0.01701065,-0.06231624,0.009594054,0.06722455,-0.05100789,0.014761009,0.049901113,0.