	('2ea6e9ef-248e-4516-9898-bf909bb15180', 'High Performance Teams Remote Workforce', 'CORP081', 'This corporate training program on High Performance Teams Remote Workforce helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying high performance teams remote workforce in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765255003947-tofvlrz62b7.jpg', 'Active', '3 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 6, 6, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:58:50.516751+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of High Performance Teams Remote Workforce in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong high performance teams remote workforce is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to high performance teams remote workforce in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in high performance teams remote workforce.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: High Performance Teams Remote Workforce, Collaboration, Teamwork, Facilitation, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.012259564,0.014273064,0.08448078,0.02731463,0.003833038,-0.01757348,-0.01040616,0.07275692,0.014494734,0.04773287,0.05256034,0.0052277097,-0.015430672,-0.026551101,0.01070172,0.017585794,-0.009457906,-0.04674767,-0.0015139731,0.021218713,0.02628017,0.021588163,-0.0052800486,0.037363656,-0.057190776,0.02765945,-0.036846425,0.06640238,0.00422096,0.006939492,0.0032080528,-0.01688384,-0.017979873,-0.04081185,0.0343588,0.012955361,-0.023743285,0.06147639,0.004267141,0.01342333,-0.008023211,-0.019408412,-0.0018164598,0.06571274,-0.018583307,0.0021489644,0.021994557,0.0029802255,0.032930262,0.018127654,-0.039974432,0.023718655,-0.010738