	('859fd2bb-0764-4f6b-8e4d-73293a4d3950', 'Business Ethics', 'CORP119', 'This corporate training program on Business Ethics helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying business ethics in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765251663014-osb07dbbmn7.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:56:11.788998+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Business Ethics in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong business ethics is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to business ethics in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in business ethics.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Business Ethics, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.024555998,0.03198372,0.058015887,0.023349285,-0.002218651,0.00096727314,0.0030665707,0.060687054,0.030976173,0.03854448,0.05810961,-0.05609452,0.0059925537,-0.0360139,0.034092534,0.040723592,-0.007685465,0.00033279762,0.008499702,0.019037927,0.04212947,0.014632844,-0.0038427324,0.10300397,-0.052907865,0.011645353,-0.008113086,0.013344123,-0.009782566,-0.015394361,0.05028356,-0.015265489,-0.01017504,-0.030507546,0.014972597,-0.002482253,-0.020326648,0.0022391533,0.0521112,0.0022274374,-0.024204528,-0.02495433,0.0062795873,0.036623113,-0.053423353,0.00068902655,-0.027110009,0.0088511715,0.039294284,0.025657268,-0.022400318,-0.0024163523,0.005122667,-0.022505758,-0.047916997,0.006121426,-0.030484116,-0.004888354,-0.053329628,0.0287502,0.044074267,-0.027461478,-0.016308181,0.047916997,0.009442812,0.025399525,-0.01230143,-0.009108916,-0.0264305,-0.046042494,0.0