	('b2f1b4d4-796c-444e-9734-ea9619afdf5b', 'Telework And Telecommuting', 'CORP026', 'This corporate training program on Telework And Telecommuting helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying telework and telecommuting in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765253979536-r9ly2ea9rnm.jpg', 'Active', '4 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:01:14.34115+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Telework And Telecommuting in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong telework and telecommuting is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to telework and telecommuting in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in telework and telecommuting.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Telework And Telecommuting, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.0010782545,0.012111685,0.07640743,0.008342906,0.005779004,-0.0019803392,0.03603934,0.05733074,0.04341331,0.07147467,0.02760835,-0.016899733,0.005027136,-0.03120725,0.021115229,-0.009701932,-0.013992929,-0.008173028,0.045426685,0.048874583,0.03800238,0.03077941,-0.007996858,0.038354717,-0.032415275,-0.010714909,-0.04756589,0.058589097,0.0019300049,-0.025481727,0.016547393,-0.026148656,-0.054763693,-0.029042877,0.046257198,0.016320888,-0.0062886383,0.060048793,0.021203313,0.014659857,-0.0092363395,-0.007562725,0.05793475,0.059897788,-0.049579263,0.00078725955,-0.0076445183,0.028816372,0.026853336,0.02919388,-0.012961076,-0.008701538,-0.001356666,-0.018623682,-0.060350798,-0.0057852957,-0.028539535,0.010721201,-0.058790434,-0.01702557,0.03991508,-0.04897525,0.022876928,0.06