	('076676b1-7c2b-40e8-84bd-44b5c10c5e2f', 'Managing Workplace Harassment', 'CORP042', 'This corporate training program on Managing Workplace Harassment helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying managing workplace harassment in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256215182-9hjf5llyyv.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:59:22.152859+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Managing Workplace Harassment in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong managing workplace harassment is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to managing workplace harassment in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in managing workplace harassment.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Managing Workplace Harassment, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.012335709,0.045480613,0.048640613,0.027550532,-0.03581335,-0.01341245,0.03354283,0.008262819,0.014442377,0.057535432,0.060859285,-0.0022617418,-0.009398079,-0.01151645,-0.009427338,0.010346078,-0.006641855,0.017438527,0.021347566,0.012008006,0.041805647,0.09166345,0.0069285957,0.08286226,-0.03941809,0.031319126,-0.03209157,0.05247943,-0.0030692976,0.043654833,0.020680454,-0.024694826,-0.06699203,0.007150966,0.06806877,-0.012593191,-0.017028896,0.020797491,0.0029683532,0.017719416,-0.011276524,-0.0007252642,0.025420455,0.03326194,-0.015413784,0.008473486,0.011563265,0.02111349,0.020095268,0.01780134,-0.021054972,-0.007894152,0.009362967,-0.0007406253,-0.042250387,0.007940967,-0.0077420035,0.026778085,-0.035696313,-0.009029412,0.048172466,-0.01952178