	('f437f8b8-e085-41ed-a691-1b2972d04dd1', 'Creativity: Thinking Outside the Box', 'CORP016', 'This corporate training program on Creativity: Thinking Outside the Box helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying creativity: thinking outside the box in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765258383166-2jfxulgj2vj.webp', 'Active', '6 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:56:47.001955+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Creativity: Thinking Outside the Box in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong creativity: thinking outside the box is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to creativity: thinking outside the box in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in creativity: thinking outside the box.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Creativity: Thinking Outside the Box, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.009591369,0.0029158266,0.07799049,0.0117577715,0.0006096943,-0.042874616,0.03221894,0.05310205,0.011940404,0.034889154,0.07728515,-0.0143965,0.017381601,0.0018326254,0.041866988,0.026223546,-0.005201885,-0.02947315,0.02414531,0.009692132,0.013073987,0.01352742,-0.01768389,0.07587447,0.0071352734,-0.0017035229,-0.009188318,0.050457023,0.015731608,0.005321541,0.02773499,-0.016373971,-0.038365476,-0.03572045,0.0136029925,0.021374332,-0.02838995,0.018830068,0.033579238,0.0087222885,-0.01850259,-0.040960122,0.050104354,0.042471565,0.025732327,-0.022293793,0.025946448,0.0066377562,-0.00022986537,0.02844033,-0.012582768,0.058795154,0.0036148692,-0.04398301,-0.048038714,0.008117711,-0.044612776,0.0