	('f457fcd2-e0a4-4799-9616-8366b438ed00', 'Ten Soft Skills You Need', 'CORP027', 'This corporate training program on Ten Soft Skills You Need helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying ten soft skills you need in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765255999209-uyjihckuc7.jpg', 'Active', '4 weeks', 2, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:01:16.132118+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Ten Soft Skills You Need in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong ten soft skills you need is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to ten soft skills you need in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in ten soft skills you need.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Ten Soft Skills You Need, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.009830913,0.04651426,0.036784466,0.018616939,0.034357637,-0.017740585,0.015830578,0.0683108,0.01623505,0.021459479,0.051412866,-0.048356853,0.011010623,-0.03968318,0.05671594,-0.015830578,0.0073085814,-0.0038874238,0.03341387,0.00025121492,0.032402687,0.020324709,-0.02936915,0.083635785,0.00363182,0.041503303,0.026110904,0.051143218,0.013246452,0.023369484,0.005640135,-0.02116736,-0.041143775,-0.0046149115,0.051727455,0.019043881,-0.006752433,0.04100895,0.014381221,-0.013212747,0.017369818,0.03590811,0.026200786,0.018347291,0.0070220805,0.009684853,0.016414816,-0.0399753,0.03175104,0.034110457,-0.051817335,-0.015291283,-0.016774345,-0.00303073,-0.006729962,0.01743723,-0.037997883,0.022403246,-0.0135947475,-0.0036795703,0.045907553,-0.027167024,-0.000924808,0.055862054,0.02972868,0.025009