	('b4591a88-9843-4109-931a-f0f4a7a339ae', 'Goal Setting and Getting Things Done', 'CORP059', 'This corporate training program on Goal Setting and Getting Things Done helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying goal setting and getting things done in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256738256-n59d061trj.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:58:43.586436+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Goal Setting and Getting Things Done in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong goal setting and getting things done is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to goal setting and getting things done in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in goal setting and getting things done.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Goal Setting and Getting Things Done, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.02738349,0.04229623,0.07031985,-0.0026509233,-0.025652759,-0.012399624,0.00278873,0.067901574,0.008197266,0.008463988,0.055193737,-0.0116290925,-0.046729747,-0.07340198,0.0065198787,-0.000997986,-0.003396264,-0.029967733,0.03003886,0.05410314,0.05253837,0.01718877,0.010603693,0.064203024,-0.038170926,0.0056930394,0.03243343,0.06486686,0.011824689,0.016287843,0.0065139513,-0.008807763,-0.032077804,-0.03212522,0.061737325,0.032765355,0.007675675,0.075298674,-0.011919524,-0.01318201,-0.016216716,0.014841614,0.01913288,0.0069821975,-0.0032510485,0.0010535531,0.041561265,0.0040304703,0.028189585,0.010574058,-0.033974495,0.04480935,-0.02984919,0.025842428,-0.006318355,0.009815381,-0.027786538,-0.01