	('5c822117-4469-48fe-80ae-9f62d00483c7', 'Personal Productivity', 'CORP067', 'This corporate training program on Personal Productivity helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying personal productivity in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765256800430-hp4kx5br2rn.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 6, 6, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:17.74441+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Personal Productivity in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong personal productivity is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to personal productivity in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in personal productivity.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Personal Productivity, Time Management, Prioritization, Planning, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.004195998,0.03828809,0.073563345,0.011881862,-0.000294222,-0.03105729,0.02049982,0.09791709,0.046874665,0.02053748,0.053377364,-0.025370568,-0.02046216,-0.04659849,0.027165715,0.0017512094,0.0015613381,-0.032890096,-0.008209971,0.028571703,0.047025308,0.011530364,-0.011932076,0.06080902,-0.023575421,0.020399394,-0.0091703115,0.053678647,-0.009559469,-0.012854756,0.00054607604,-0.016959742,-0.013683285,-0.016043337,0.030856434,0.017989125,0.020575142,0.047452126,0.027617639,0.019746613,-0.028446168,0.009766602,0.025081838,0.046422742,-0.011969736,-0.0032325191,0.027969137,0.023726063,0.030555151,0.03133347,-0.009138928,0.02469268,-0.0036875824,0.026412506,-0.05357822,0.029149164,-0.017512094,-0.0034490665,-0.053377364,0.015528645,0.07441699,-0.04707552,0.044188224,0.092