	('99c22d67-7fb9-4ddd-b6cb-42f35a3ed1d4', 'Work-Life Balance', 'CORP073', 'This corporate training program on Work-Life Balance helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying work-life balance in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765258203221-m8gzuvmrb2.jpg', 'Active', '3 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:01:42.810938+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Work-Life Balance in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong work-life balance is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to work-life balance in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in work-life balance.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Work-Life Balance, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.028240211,0.039837588,0.065232255,0.022405654,-0.016308064,-0.034505185,0.0105572,0.030679246,0.0398615,0.032544393,0.048589423,-0.028838014,-0.022955634,-0.04270704,0.040052798,0.019643804,-0.009236055,0.005649238,0.002439036,0.028072827,0.012219092,0.025705526,-0.014658128,0.08890525,-0.018699275,-0.008632274,8.3972634e-05,0.018161254,-0.022907808,-0.022620864,0.050645865,-0.020456817,0.0064383377,-0.0018337605,0.034266066,0.018376462,0.019368816,0.025131635,0.036872484,7.96876e-06,-0.050071973,0.0145385675,0.023254534,0.070158154,0.000117972675,0.028814102,0.00070540747,0.065088786,0.051698,0.025585966,-0.024091458,0.01547114,0.016463494,-0.006091612,-0.026518539,0.03931152,-0.022596952,-0.0058315676,-0.040052798,0.027953265,0.056097828,-0.02336214,0.026470715,0.060928077,-0.011316409,0.022345874,-0.0030203995,-0.019273167,-0.025657702,-0.