	('7b419c60-6509-4abb-a476-701667f233d9', 'Overcoming Sales Objections', 'CORP088', 'This corporate training program on Overcoming Sales Objections helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying overcoming sales objections in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765254316643-beawhr4zhou.jpg', 'Active', '2 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 6, 6, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:12.256358+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Overcoming Sales Objections in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong overcoming sales objections is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to overcoming sales objections in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in overcoming sales objections.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Overcoming Sales Objections, Sales Skills, Customer Focus, Negotiation, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.013835483,0.019031558,0.057231415,0.021356119,-0.033836644,-0.013636591,-0.02354394,0.028441677,0.0489525,0.02804389,0.08820897,-0.055689994,-0.020945903,-0.03080353,0.021169657,0.04261279,0.01766417,0.013599298,-0.0033283473,0.022089537,0.08801008,0.051811587,0.006706418,0.046192862,-0.046192862,-0.0011964648,0.016781583,0.025358837,-0.013736037,-0.015103425,0.030082542,-0.035427786,-0.058573943,0.008477807,0.014469454,0.0064702327,-0.003663979,-0.001765174,0.02290997,0.04134485,0.0075952206,0.028914047,0.020212485,0.010889383,-0.007327958,0.08084994,0.009142855,-0.02866543,-0.016532967,-0.0022142367,-0.02074701,0.027347766,0.02136855,0.012437018,-0.04383101,-0.009391472,-0.012132463,-0.0028653,-0.037988532,-0.01260483