	('0fe49b7b-ad37-4d46-bbd2-214ab7004722', 'Social Media In The Workplace', 'CORP011', 'This corporate training program on Social Media In The Workplace helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying social media in the workplace in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765195493966-6tnfj1g91vw.jpg', 'Active', '3 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:53.852576+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Social Media In The Workplace in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong social media in the workplace is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to social media in the workplace in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in social media in the workplace.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Social Media In The Workplace, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.00091355835,0.026093233,-5.8573256e-05,0.03142995,0.033082914,-0.023696434,0.007957846,0.0445356,0.025927937,0.038584925,0.048738852,-0.046519157,-0.010720659,-0.015573291,0.0011858548,0.010165734,-0.019823773,-0.022669233,0.03872661,0.023731854,0.034546968,0.06309603,-0.019410532,0.084915176,-0.024558337,0.02052038,-0.0058680256,0.042906247,-0.017604077,0.031052127,0.0034092402,-0.025172295,-0.053508837,-0.014168271,0.047227573,0.0025266751,-0.025479274,0.03161886,0.022822723,0.013991168,-0.023141509,0.019445952,0.018147195,0.027935108,-0.039718386,0.010248383,-0.020945428,0.0044098743,0.06866889,0.035538748,-0.049730632,0.0062635564,-0.00957539,-0.020048104,-0.0770754,0.0070723286,-0.029564459,0.013766837,-0.048644397,0.013141071,0.06309603,-0.