	('e6a9e716-e3e9-4840-9ee0-18d48d3698c9', 'Safety In The Workplace', 'CORP136', 'This corporate training program on Safety In The Workplace helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying safety in the workplace in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765210040093-6os4u52uvph.jpg', 'Active', '6 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:39.741999+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Safety In The Workplace in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong safety in the workplace is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to safety in the workplace in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in safety in the workplace.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Safety In The Workplace, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.007535942,0.031751126,0.051155884,0.02760461,-0.01841472,-0.020709282,0.0020950967,0.04409749,0.017517861,0.03265963,0.060706846,-0.015013646,-0.004082454,-0.036340244,0.029491507,0.012055177,0.0012390043,0.0066856733,0.027767675,-0.0077630687,0.023411505,0.00942284,-0.014407976,0.0899654,-0.045704845,-0.0055733356,0.018100237,0.008211498,-0.0031826834,0.017843992,0.053718336,-0.020231733,-0.04933887,0.010535177,0.04817412,0.005186056,-0.004396937,0.026067138,-0.0159338,-0.016574413,-0.009923683,0.034756184,0.021804146,0.03384768,-0.0011450963,-0.0009718395,0.017366445,-0.0069128,0.028909132,0.0057946383,-0.022141926,-0.022095336,0.015759088,0.011024373,-0.035082314,0.0040620705,-0.010867131,0.034034036,-0.029654572,-0.006965214,0.06895328,-0.012812266,-0.03825044,0.04840707,0.021338247,-0.0081