	('41e01672-a7a0-4ed3-8c1f-ee2f5305f634', 'Trust Building and Resilience Development', 'CORP115', 'This corporate training program on Trust Building and Resilience Development helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying trust building and resilience development in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765251968308-n0auj287gh.jpg', 'Active', '4 weeks', 1, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:01:32.04162+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Trust Building and Resilience Development in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong trust building and resilience development is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to trust building and resilience development in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in trust building and resilience development.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Trust Building and Resilience Development, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.0128756305,0.034060396,0.087752014,0.04552371,-0.013770099,-0.011816393,0.008909372,0.042322457,-0.031188685,0.03728519,0.05013728,-0.014899953,0.028293435,-0.04863081,0.034272246,0.032954082,0.013511173,-0.004831304,-0.009068257,0.01684189,0.036014106,-0.009797955,-0.03474302,0.03594349,-0.032883465,0.010627692,-0.013369942,0.03648488,0.004787169,-0.012652013,0.026339727,-0.020349147,-0.006396623,0.0034395824,0.052114528,0.015617881,-0.011887008,0.018324824,0.013746561,0.024103558,-0.0065084314,-0.019642986,-0.015735574,0.052349914,-0.0052020373,0.01108081,-0.0029482134,0.007455861,0.00893291,0.017818743,-0.007926634,0.004378185,-0.013699483,0.029329134