	('a92a3d11-ea54-48b8-89c5-3834eb2902c3', 'Responsibility In the Workplace', 'CORP134', 'This corporate training program on Responsibility In the Workplace helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying responsibility in the workplace in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765211100403-03zweb5usvks.jpg', 'Active', '3 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 06:00:35.8114+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Responsibility In the Workplace in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong responsibility in the workplace is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to responsibility in the workplace in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in responsibility in the workplace.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Responsibility In the Workplace, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[0.017262861,0.040369254,0.06192746,0.04630591,0.0074149985,-0.03464213,0.0014492422,0.06211371,-0.00062676816,0.029427184,0.08637251,-0.015679754,-0.008258935,-0.04234814,-0.009743099,-0.01257174,0.0068969964,0.00061621895,0.019916896,0.035433684,0.0020647338,0.014213051,-0.009696537,0.0684927,-0.055269096,-0.0033757451,-0.022454524,0.017146457,-0.0043593673,0.002814091,0.042674072,-0.020335954,-0.029031407,0.0019366882,0.026680026,-0.0181359,-0.017577155,0.018869251,0.005884273,-0.0004688939,-0.019241747,0.019614242,0.052661624,0.048750415,-0.031662162,0.039018955,-0.0067689507,-0.008340418,0.035270717,0.03815756,-0.0004477955,0.007706011,0.022687335,-0.012595021,-0.06355713,0.005674744,-0.0047376836,0.035899304,-0.061322156,-0.00250