	('1dfb5c07-7e2d-47b9-b90a-75f70f350003', 'Civility In The Workplace', 'CORP122', 'This corporate training program on Civility In The Workplace helps participants understand key principles, explore practical workplace examples, and build confidence applying civility in the workplace in their daily roles.', 'https://dpooleduinyyzxgrcwko.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/course-images/courses/1765251140287-g6wswoat76l.jpg', 'Active', '5 weeks', 0, 0, 0, 3, 3, 'de3175cc-13f8-4cba-986a-363a3057a90d', '2025-12-04 00:00:00+00', '2026-01-19 05:56:24.178939+00', NULL, '["Explain the core concepts and importance of Civility In The Workplace in a professional environment.", "Recognize common workplace situations where strong civility in the workplace is critical to success.", "Apply tools, techniques, and best practices related to civility in the workplace in realistic scenarios.", "Create a personal action plan to strengthen your day-to-day performance in civility in the workplace.", "Demonstrate growth in key skills developed in this course: Civility In The Workplace, Professionalism, Problem Solving."]', NULL, NULL, 'Corporate Training', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'soft', NULL, '[-0.012056378,0.017261442,0.04795921,0.030843023,0.0042336527,-0.032053504,0.0028128524,0.040817376,0.030721975,0.061395533,0.052776918,-0.03161773,-0.00023698923,-0.025250606,0.032513484,0.026073733,0.00746866,0.005389661,0.03299768,0.01693461,0.025759008,0.047426596,-0.019476619,0.08667035,-0.038057484,0.018871378,-0.013605792,0.045562457,0.0003202097,-0.004841919,0.017164603,-0.023059638,-0.037452243,-0.020977614,-0.0044515394,0.0031169853,-0.00744445,0.008763873,0.032804,0.025347445,-0.046240326,-0.005707412,0.030237783,0.010488807,-0.0041519455,-0.018931903,0.025492704,0.030843023,0.013278963,0.010803532,-0.023785926,0.0038190635,-0.017430909,-0.025613751,-0.031375635,0.017273545,-0.005537945,-0.0061522634,-0.041301567,-0.021958102,0.0502107,-0.046361372,-0.016280953,0.0324892